<HEADLINE> Goodfellow Named AP Graphics Head </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Kris Goodfellow has been named director of  
graphics at The Associated Press. 
</P>
<P>
	Goodfellow joined the AP last year as an artist in New York. She  
worked briefly in the Paris bureau before returning to AP's 
international headquarters. 
</P>
<P>
	Goodfellow, 29, is a native of Dover, N.H., and a graduate of  
Northwestern University. She previously was a graphics editor at 
The New York Times. 
</P>
</TEXT>
