point in the new millennium, the journey would continue.'' 
</P>
<P>
	But many residents urged Knight and his artistic endeavor to  
take a hike. 
</P>
<P>
	``It's an embarrassment, and unfortunately it will be a  
long-lasting embarrassment,'' art dealer Charles Campbell said 
before the vote. 
</P>
